#: ../../../sound/designs/oss-emulation.rst:11
msgid ""
"ALSA provides a powerful OSS emulation on the kernel. The OSS emulation for "
"PCM, mixer and sequencer devices is implemented as add-on kernel modules, "
"snd-pcm-oss, snd-mixer-oss and snd-seq-oss. When you need to access the OSS "
"PCM, mixer or sequencer devices, the corresponding module has to be loaded."
